VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT document\.write\(|innerHTML\s?=\s?.+
WHEN EXPR MISSING:DOMPurify\.sanitize|sanitizeHtml|textContent|innerText|escapeHtml|encodeHTML && MISSING:test|example|spec
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects potential DOM-based cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted Data in 'document.write'.
